message.body: Hey man do you have a sledgehammer over there that I could borrow for an hour?
I'm sure mine has been stolen from michaels yard by now. It was in the van but I haven't seen it in a while . It's not at my house
There's a small chance that it is in the yard or in the van
Yeah I checked the yard and michael said maybe you had it or it was in the van. Im asking milan if he has one...
